name: The Winged Dragon of Ra (Anime)
desc:
Requires 3 Tributes to Normal Summon this card (cannot be Normal Set). This card's Normal Summon cannot be negated. When this card is Normal Summoned, card effects cannot be activated. Control of this card cannot switch. This card cannot be Tributed by your opponent. This card cannot be targeted by card effects that would leave it from the field. This card cannot be destroyed by card effects. Card effects affect it for 1 turn. If this card is Special Summoned: Send it to the Graveyard during the End Phase. This card's ATK and DEF is equal to the ATK and DEF of the Tributes. When this card is targeted for an attack by a DIVINE Divine-Beast-Type monster, except "The Winged Dragon of Ra" or "The Wicked Avatar": You can negate that attack. When this card is Special Summoned from the Graveyard: you can activate 1 of the following effects and it will gain the following effects.
● Point-to-Point Transfer: pay LP until you have 1 left;
- It is treated as a Fusion Monster. ("De-Fusion" returns its ATK and DEF to LP.)
- It gains ATK and DEF to the amount paid.
- During either player's turn: you can Tribute 2 monsters; this card gains their combined ATK and DEF.
● Egyptian God Phoenix:
- This card cannot be destroyed by battle and you take no Battle Damage involving this card.
- You can attack all monsters your opponent controls plus a direct attack.
- During either player's turn: you can pay 1000 Life Points to target 1 monster on the field; Destroy it, ignoring effects that would prevent it from being destroyed.

name: Boss Duel
desc:

Start=> 1=> 2=> 3

● Pay 1000 Life Points to target 1 other monster on the field; destroy it and banish it instead of sending it to the Graveyard.
